01%2900469-6&amp;pmid=11804754">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">14.</div><div id="b14-0291781" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Singh A, Danrad R, Hahn PF, Blake MA, Mueller PR, Novelline RA. MR imaging of the acute abdomen and pelvis: acute appendicitis and beyond. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2007;27:1419–1431.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.275065021">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17848700/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=MR+imaging+of+the+acute+abdomen+and+pelvis%3A+acute+appendicitis+and+beyond&amp;author=A+Singh&amp;author=R+Danrad&amp;author=PF+Hahn&amp;author=MA+Blake&amp;author=PR+Mueller&amp;author=RA+Novelline&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1419-1431&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.275065021&amp;pmid=17848700">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="b15-0291781" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Heverhagen JT, Ishaque N, Zielke A, et al. Feasibility of MRI in the diagnosis of acute diverticulitis: initial results. <em>MAGMA</em> 2001;12:4–9.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/BF02678267">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11255086/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Feasibility+of+MRI+in+the+diagnosis+of+acute+diverticulitis%3A+initial+results&amp;author=JT+Heverhagen&amp;author=N+Ishaque&amp;author=A+Zielke&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;journal=MAGMA&amp;pages=4-9&amp;doi=10.1007%2FBF02678267&amp;pmid=11255086">Goo